# Verify Work

Verify the work completed in the previous step.

## Verification Criteria

1. Check that deliverables meet requirements
2. Verify no regressions were introduced
3. Confirm all acceptance criteria are satisfied

## Instructions

1. Review the completed work
2. Run verification checks
3. Use `next` to proceed to closure if verified
4. Use `repeat` to return to continuation for fixes
5. Use `escalate` if issues require special attention
